42:48.933 --> 42:58.843 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: If a man puts family or
friends ahead of fatherland, I
count him absolutely good

42:58.843 --> 43:01.279 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for nothing.

43:01.279 --> 43:06.184 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: A political
leader, King Creon, declares
that the security of the state
must

43:06.184 --> 43:10.455 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
take precedence over individual
need, and orders that the body
of a slain rebel not

43:10.455 --> 43:12.156 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
be given burial rites.

43:12.156 --> 43:14.992 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ACTOR: You dare to
disobey the law?

43:14.992 --> 43:20.965 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JULIETTE BINOCHE, Actress: What
