43:26.471 --> 43:30.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The rebel's
sister, named Antigone, and
played here by Juliette Binoche,
defies

43:30.641 --> 43:34.512 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
