brother, leading to her own
death.

43:34.512 --> 43:39.717 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JULIETTE BINOCHE: She has this
need of remembering where we
come from, the origin of where
we

43:39.717 --> 43:42.720 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
