43:42.720 --> 43:49.727 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So the play is an immense -- is
reaching immense subjects of
what we go through.

43:49.727 --> 43:54.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The playwright
