this?

44:17.655 --> 44:23.394 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JULIETTE BINOCHE: Well, because
the myths put you into a
teaching of what is -- what

44:23.394 --> 44:26.264 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
