It's about transformation

44:26.264 --> 44:28.199 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: That's
a big question.

44:28.199 --> 44:32.003 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JULIETTE BINOCHE: It's a big
question, but we here, all --
all of us, we're trying to

44:32.003 --> 44:38.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
