doing it.

46:13.070 --> 46:17.808 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The production of
"Antigone" directed by Ivo van
Hove was a spare one in

46:17.808 --> 46:21.045 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
its language, its
